  <brief_title>Safety, Immunogenicity and Reactogenicity of Recombinant Hepatitis B Vaccine (Adjuvanted &amp; New Formulation) and Engerix™-B</brief_title>
  <official_title>Study to Assess the Safety, Immunogenicity and Reactogenicity of GSK Biologicals' (Previously SmithKline Beecham Biologicals') Adjuvanted Recombinant Hepatitis B Vaccine, Recombinant Hepatitis B Vaccine New Formulation and Engerix™-B</official_title>
